<p>This what I have come up with:</p>  <pre><code>Create table Users  (     UserName varchar(35) not null,     Password varchar(35) not null,     UserId int Foreign key references UserDetails (UserId) ) </code></pre>  <p>This the procedure to confirm the username and password if it's correct:</p>  <pre><code>CREATE PROCEDURE sp_Login      @Username varchar(35),      @Password varchar(35) AS BEGIN      SELECT @Username = Username       FROM Users      WHERE Username = @Username;       SELECT @Password = Password      FROM Users      WHERE Password = @Password; </code></pre>